{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0cc53412f2","title":"关于再令四方面军迅速北上致朱、张、徐、陈电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c946f06491","index":0,"year":1936,"month":9,"day":27,"articleId":"0cc53412f2"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3b795a1ed6","type":"paragraph","text":"关于再令四方面军迅速北上","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"0cc53412f2"},{"id":"f52b126b2a","type":"paragraph","text":"致朱、张、徐、陈电”","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"0cc53412f2"},{"id":"a73fb280c6","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年9月27日）朱、张，徐、陈：","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"0cc53412f2"},{"id":"e6f2c42fd3","type":"paragraph","text":"（甲）中央明令已下，请速令通渭部队仍回占通渭，其余跟即北上。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"0cc53412f2"},{"id":"9b53248291","type":"paragraph","text":"（乙）侯得复电，我二师即出庄浪、秦安，一师出瓦、隆、静、界线策应。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"0cc53412f2"},{"id":"c5a28f1cce","type":"paragraph","text":"（丙）胡宗南之补充旅已由会宁退兰州，会宁城仅留二个连，甚恐。有袭占该城可能。胡之余部不敢走西兰大道向宝鸡、天水进，我二方面军足以箱制之。二师出庄浪后，胡更不敢冒进。四方面军现有充分时间进入降、静、会、定大道，敌无阻止可能。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"0cc53412f2"},{"id":"937e386e1e","type":"paragraph","text":"（丁）兰、凉线虽有五六百里，但沿途人户稀少，粮食不足，且中有大雪山。此为邓发亲历函告者。敌如先占要点，我将遇绝大","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"0cc53412f2"},{"id":"2fcd6b37fa","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东、周恩来、彭德怀给朱德、张国秦、徐向前、陈昌浩的电报。四方面军领导人接此电报后，即于当日致电中央，表示“尊重你们的指示和意见”，并说红四方面军“决仍照原计划东出会宁，会合一方面军为目的…·决不再改变”。10月9日，四方面军到达会宁与一方面军会合；22日，二方面军到甘肃省隆德西北之将台堡（今属宁夏）与一方面军会合。至此，二、四两个方面军也胜利地完成了长征困难。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"0cc53412f2"},{"id":"a0c21f8e91","type":"paragraph","text":"（戊）请速决速电。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"0cc53412f2"},{"id":"ab5145acbf","type":"paragraph","text":"毛周彭廿七日十八时","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"0cc53412f2"}],"page":{"id":"aa927f32c6","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"0cc53412f2","start":177,"end":178}}}},"__N_SSG":true}